metadata.name: Eternal Viking #1
metadata.description: Introducing “Sacrifice to Mint”, a first-of-its-kind public sale. Instead of minting for ETH, simply swap an asset in your vault for an Eternal Vikings Genesis Collection NFT. Eternal Vikings is a genesis collection of 5,000 Vikings with a goal of educating the community about virtual real estate, using the project funds to raid as many lands as possible and monetize them via 6 smart contracts that allow land rental and advertising.
